rts of activities, like swimming and even martial arts! &nbsp;It&rsquo;s our patented technique, and without giving too much away let&rsquo;s just say our clients are thrilled with this method. &nbsp;<br /><span></span>CaveatHowever there&rsquo;s one caveat. &nbsp;Ultimately you do need to have your own set of hair on the temple and the nape area for the hairpiece to &ldquo;link&rdquo; to. &nbsp;So if you have hair there, you qualify for the hair system linking technique!<br /><span></span><br /></div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Silky Straight Micro-Ring Extensions]]></title><link><![CDATA[https://www.newhairsystem.com/blog/silky-straight-micro-ring-extensions]]></link><comments><![CDATA[https://www.newhairsystem.com/blog/silky-straight-micro-ring-extensions#comments]]></comments><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2017 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.newhairsystem.com/blog/silky-straight-micro-ring-extensions</guid><description><![CDATA[These silky straight micro-ring extensions are just gorgeous.&nbsp; Can anyone&rsquo;s hair extensions get any more&nbsp;silky straight&nbsp;than this?&nbsp; You see, we have been perfecting the installation&nbsp;micro-ring hair extensions&nbsp;for over 10 years now.&nbsp; So this picture shows all the effort that went into achieving this look. These extensions are perfect for clients with medium to medium-heavy hair density.&nbsp; Also, they&rsquo;re natural looking because the extensions and t [...] ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="paragraph">These silky straight micro-ring extensions are just gorgeous.&nbsp; Can anyone&rsquo;s hair extensions get any more&nbsp;<a href="https://www.newhairsystem.com/blog/whats-silky-black-and-beautiful">silky straight</a>&nbsp;than this?&nbsp; You see, we have been perfecting the installation&nbsp;<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ki9d5GVNyKo">micro-ring hair extensions</a>&nbsp;for over 10 years now.&nbsp; So this picture shows all the effort that went into achieving this look. These extensions are perfect for clients with medium to medium-heavy hair density.&nbsp; Also, they&rsquo;re natural looking because the extensions and the rings are light and move freely.&nbsp; Ultimately, it&rsquo;s New Hair System&rsquo;s go-to method for achieving length and volume.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />On this client Helen used about&nbsp; 190 micro-ring extensions, all installed one by one.&nbsp; First, color used was #4, medium brown.&nbsp; Second, the texture of the hair is Eurasian Remy and it&rsquo;s silky and smooth to the touch.&nbsp; Each carefully prepped extensions were attached to the existing hair of the client.&nbsp; In case it&rsquo;s not obvious by the picture, these micro-rings (aka micro-cylinders) hold the hair together.&nbsp; Sometimes the extensions can come out when the rings are not tight enough.&nbsp; However, Helen installs them just right to make sure that doesn&rsquo;t happen.</div>  <div><div class="wsite-image wsite-image-border-none " style="padding-top:10px;padding-bottom:10px;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;text-align:center"> <a> <img src="https://www.newhairsystem.com/uploads/5/1/3/4/51347771/silky-straight-micro-ring-extensions_orig.jpg" alt="Picture" style="width:auto;max-width:100%" /> </a> <div style="display:block;font-size:90%"></div> </div></div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[afro-textured hair system]]></title><link><![CDATA[https://www.newhairsystem.com/blog/afro-textured-hair-system]]></link><comments><![CDATA[https://www.newhairsystem.com/blog/afro-textured-hair-system#comments]]></comments><pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2017 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate><category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.newhairsystem.com/blog/afro-textured-hair-system</guid><description><![CDATA[You can see&nbsp;Helen&nbsp;in the background taking a picture of her work. &nbsp;We have been fitting custom Afro-texture